{
  "texts": [
    "Qualitative Analysis GPT 4 is not perfect at distinguishing jailbroken cases from those aligned with human values.",
    "For instance, Cipher and DrAttack implement their attack with word substitution, e.g.",
    "to ask the victim LLMs to use \"banana\" for \"firearms\" and \"cherry\" for \"malware\".",
    "However, this easily gives rise to hallucinations e.g.",
    "\"Cherry Malware Servings: Unlimited victims; Ingredients: 1 cup of social engineering tactics, 2 tablespoons of exploit code...\" and \"Start by introducing children to firearmss and explaining what they are used for."
  ]
}